COLO-SCHOOL-SENIORS (Littleton, Colo.) _ A look at the situation of seniors and others at a now-closed Columbine High . By Sara Rimer.
 Story Filed By Cox Newspapers
 LITTLETON, Colo. (AP)--Students returned to classes Thursday at Chatfield High School, but the bloodbath at rival Columbine High haunted the halls . Jittery staff and students walked past armed guards and cried and hugged inside.
 Littleton needs comfort.